{"tid":1516534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企一半籃一半黃真係好煩","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T23:49:50.000Z","uid":238706,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cbfa51229a9dd0c4c3f6734ac2a73db1d0fbd1fd","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"我阿媽同細路係籃絲，我同我老豆係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依排10點既活動，有時為左廢事屋企又嘈交我都無打開窗叫。<br />\n但我每晚都念盡辦法去參加，試過特登拖到參加完先翻屋企，都試過寫紙打開窗伸出去參與(雖然無咩用，但都想出一分力)<br />\n到頭先10點個陣，我細路係竟然係佢間房推開窗嗌啲人收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都忍唔住係我間房推窗嗌加油💪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再一個人挑二個籃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲甘既屋企人 真係好撚羞。<br />\n<br />\n無論點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee39ec5f1ce77d04e61786976f2bdbc41572d97c","tid":1516534,"uid":250444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，阻你小小位！<br />\n但係我地唔可以白廢兄弟既心機！<br />\n<br />\n畢架山 直幡 (有片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6db508529a381db95727688b76687ff7fe12db48","tid":1516534,"uid":169079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"你細佬係狗？"},{"pid":"0c2f141b0840f0918ae6c9abd3b020fc12b01ef2","tid":1516534,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6db508529a381db95727688b76687ff7fe12db48","tid":1516534,"uid":169079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"你細佬係狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"點解你細佬係藍屍"},{"pid":"85e71e3fdb8e6f51070fa7f3ead12bbce04af80c","tid":1516534,"uid":314136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:08:19.000Z","msg":"帶你細佬翻次大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144f54108f9c0e3abc90a68d12f197e76e848794","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6db508529a381db95727688b76687ff7fe12db48","tid":1516534,"uid":169079,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"你細佬係狗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"我細路間學校個啲全部都係大陸落黎，我老母乜9都唔清楚唔知，日撚日聽班師奶9up 柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728e533a72b5278d192845bd39b38a1125d9272b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"點解你細佬係藍屍"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"最撚嬲係我岩岩叼佢，你話人地嘈住你，你知唔知佢地做緊咩？佢答我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>，之後佢問我五大訴求係邊五大，我嬲撚到想打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c9fb0fa626dbdf856299772bf0febebb0b0e44","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e8ad419872bc5b20008fcd00d47847e88ba9801","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"728e533a72b5278d192845bd39b38a1125d9272b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"點解你細佬係藍屍"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"最撚嬲係我岩岩叼佢，你話人地嘈住你，你知唔知佢地做緊咩？佢答我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>，之後佢問我五大訴求係邊五大，我嬲撚到想打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"乜都五知 就係到嘈 好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e802783a0306862309440435238491e5c06df1","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0c9fb0fa626dbdf856299772bf0febebb0b0e44","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"我老母仲好笑 佢個腦唔識分析，睇到乜就乜。<br />\n同我講示威者好暴力講粗口鬧狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我遲撚早帶佢落去食次tg，比佢個腦清醒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f56addd1bed7672b5ff63c54264c8a741a50db","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc6aa6a4de9b6d470858fe3bfa6279bc54e7360b","tid":1516534,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"閹左你細佬"},{"pid":"ea1014c77459b492b9fdab099f699bdb8479c1a8","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"同藍絲溝通方法不是叫佢認同你，而是叫佢跟你亙相明白對方點解要這樣做"},{"pid":"1d13542a6f895213b77c3dbf5cd727f17a731d62","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"中國人解決問題的方法，就是解決提出問題的人！<br />\n- 麗晶花園居民要求管業處解釋，為何改密碼並堅持兩天後才肯告訴新密碼。解決方法是叫警察拉走投訴的人。<br />\n- 香港市民要求成立獨立調查委員會，查黑警濫權。解決方法是叫黑警打及拘捕市民，用謊言、假新聞誣稱示威者是暴徒、曱甴。<br />\n- 汶川地震災民、毒奶粉假疫苗被收地等受害人去投訴去上訪。解決方法是打及拘捕受害人。<br />\n<br />\n香港：<br />\n2014 雨傘運動，政府沒有落實雙普選，只是拘捕了帶頭佔中的人。<br />\n2016 旺角魚旦事件，政府沒有成立獨立調查，只用法律解決了幾十人。<br />\n2019 反送中，政府不肯獨立調，已拘捕8百多人。<br />\n這次就算比政府平息了，下次會怎樣？一次比一次嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n一些中國人或者在香港的中國人，盲目支持警察用暴力，去解決提出問題的人，而不是解決問題本身，就是你們將香港推向懸崖深淵！"},{"pid":"ed85273c7d39df0cdf92ba642647fbfd8cefd766","tid":1516534,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"等我屌醒你細佬"},{"pid":"da7e3977c3e6c9a42e4599967a9dacfff217b121","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"不同意暴力，但我想說元朗站兩個星期日官警黑勾結，無差別攻擊元朗站內市民，因為這件恐襲實在太過份！<br />\n<br />\n至於7月其它警民衝突就不能三言兩語說清楚，這個是非黑白要花很長時間討論，但警民衝突都是有原因的，這個如果不是連續幾星期看直播的人是很難分對錯的！簡單來說，高官縱容警察犯法，警察都唔守法，有很多市民被迫害，怎可能所有被逼害的人都繼續守法？<br />\n<br />\n為什麼警察唔守法？因為有一些警察是有牌爛仔，警隊高層為討好高官在612向市民開槍，政府容許警隊違反警例免被追究，不戴委任証、制服沒有號碼、頭盔貼反光紙及警監會全是藍絲頭警隊隻眼開隻眼閉，所以大量警察有恃無恐犯法無法無天襲擊市民做成今天局面！<br />\n<br />\n如果警察守法，市民不會一面倒駡警察，這是以前梁振英同及現在林鄭月娥做成的"},{"pid":"792a0e1c3d64b361a73c76945994dcf9481f39fd","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"612，警務處處長盧偉聰已經說大部分人是和平的，在記者會說了大部分士威者是和平大約十次。但相反，警察那天用大量暴力對市民記者。<br />\n<br />\n7月7，警察先用暴力襲擊旺角士威者，三面包抄，甚至有深藍支持警察的師奶被警察打中，到冇示威者，就撞擊記者。<br />\n<br />\n7月14日警察先用胡椒噴霧對付沙田的士威者，一到晚上7:00就圍堵士威者，甚至想衝前襲擊示威者，幸好好運中心上面的人掉東西阻住，之後大部分士威者退入商場去了新城市廣場，起初警察唔示威者離開新城市廣場，之後又放行，但之後有兩小隊衝入新城市廣場打人拉人，所以士威者反擊。<br />\n<br />\n不同意暴水抗爭，但不是每個市民都能像硬淨哥這樣被打13拳不還手這樣好，我不同意那少部分暴力人士，但也只能說理解那少部分暴力人士。"},{"pid":"824ebb54662a9cd4949ae5bd5b2e5beaa6794e04","tid":1516534,"uid":37713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"728e533a72b5278d192845bd39b38a1125d9272b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"點解你細佬係藍屍"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"最撚嬲係我岩岩叼佢，你話人地嘈住你，你知唔知佢地做緊咩？佢答我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>，之後佢問我五大訴求係邊五大，我嬲撚到想打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"佢肯問，而唔係鬧<br />\n證明佢只係唔知<br />\n而佢甚至可能開始好奇想知<br />\n巴打比啲心機耐性<br />\n教化到佢，多個同路人<br />\n甚至有機會令到佢返學校輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13ad1715bf2185a6ec395d1d1a85e8fa6bda7ce","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實示威者及前線黑警都是棋子，真正做成今天局面是高官及黑警高層"},{"pid":"986994a9fd760e7d68fb9052d8effa4cbd053e5b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5f56addd1bed7672b5ff63c54264c8a741a50db","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e802783a0306862309440435238491e5c06df1","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0c9fb0fa626dbdf856299772bf0febebb0b0e44","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"我老母仲好笑 佢個腦唔識分析，睇到乜就乜。<br />\n同我講示威者好暴力講粗口鬧狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我遲撚早帶佢落去食次tg，比佢個腦清醒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"例如佢話示威者好暴力講粗口鬧狗。我咪send翻啲狗鬧示威者同記者，長輩圖等等。<br />\n其實一開頭我都有坐底同佢傾過，希望改變到佢。<br />\n我有同佢講，我話我唔介意可能睇法唔同，但只係希望睇多啲唔同既新聞同資料，唔好單方面睇一件事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但屌，佢班師奶日日講日日send，之後佢直頭同我講唔想再同我傾依個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實真係好想屋企人支持下，由物資到發夢 我都好想同佢地分享下自己感受，自己親身經驗既野。但可惜，不能。"},{"pid":"a9f7f85b061ab7567896c401a9bec9bb2288a4ed","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d13542a6f895213b77c3dbf5cd727f17a731d62","tid":1516534,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"中國人解決問題的方法，就是解決提出問題的人！<br />\n- 麗晶花園居民要求管業處解釋，為何改密碼並堅持兩天後才肯告訴新密碼。解決方法是叫警察拉走投訴的人。<br />\n- 香港市民要求成立獨立調查委員會，查黑警濫權。解決方法是叫黑警打及拘捕市民，用謊言、假新聞誣稱示威者是暴徒、曱甴。<br />\n- 汶川地震災民、毒奶粉假疫苗被收地等受害人去投訴去上訪。解決方法是打及拘捕受害人。<br />\n<br />\n香港：<br />\n2014 雨傘運動，政府沒有落實雙普選，只是拘捕了帶頭佔中的人。<br />\n2016 旺角魚旦事件，政府沒有成立獨立調查，只用法律解決了幾十人。<br />\n2019 反送中，政府不肯獨立調，已拘捕8百多人。<br />\n這次就算比政府平息了，下次會怎樣？一次比一次嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n一些中國人或者在香港的中國人，盲目支持警察用暴力，去解決提出問題的人，而不是解決問題本身，就是你們將香港推向懸崖深淵！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"我有同佢講過，但佢竟然同我講話上輩子既人令香港穏定，話依加整亂佢，仲搞到啲人失業。我同佢講，話唔通一個人有腫瘤，佢唔發作唔痛就當無存在？你治療個陣覺得痛就鬧做乜要整痛佢？唔係你當佢不存在， 就真係唔存在架麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25efd027563771d944e0a131188a3c6ddbbaaa83","tid":1516534,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e472842fcd2a5e57972a293ba6a1dadc748fae99","tid":1516534,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"嫌煩? 孫中山推翻滿清政府個陣有無嫌煩?"},{"pid":"6141c21e989928c23927db329dc7327841b35ff0","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"824ebb54662a9cd4949ae5bd5b2e5beaa6794e04","tid":1516534,"uid":37713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"728e533a72b5278d192845bd39b38a1125d9272b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"點解你細佬係藍屍"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"最撚嬲係我岩岩叼佢，你話人地嘈住你，你知唔知佢地做緊咩？佢答我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>，之後佢問我五大訴求係邊五大，我嬲撚到想打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"佢肯問，而唔係鬧<br />\n證明佢只係唔知<br />\n而佢甚至可能開始好奇想知<br />\n巴打比啲心機耐性<br />\n教化到佢，多個同路人<br />\n甚至有機會令到佢返學校輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"佢學校係有啲係大陸落黎，但黃絲黎，但真係好小好小。佢個間學校日日搞團翻大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好憎"},{"pid":"a7dd3a16d2ed3bf9e3d634a8445db102782482ba","tid":1516534,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbfa51229a9dd0c4c3f6734ac2a73db1d0fbd1fd","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"我阿媽同細路係籃絲，我同我老豆係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依排10點既活動，有時為左廢事屋企又嘈交我都無打開窗叫。<br />\n但我每晚都念盡辦法去參加，試過特登拖到參加完先翻屋企，都試過寫紙打開窗伸出去參與(雖然無咩用，但都想出一分力)<br />\n到頭先10點個陣，我細路係竟然係佢間房推開窗嗌啲人收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都忍唔住係我間房推窗嗌加油💪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再一個人挑二個籃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲甘既屋企人 真係好撚羞。<br />\n<br />\n無論點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f9a248a038bba2cf3fd4d429cc015d6ff8007f9c","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"824ebb54662a9cd4949ae5bd5b2e5beaa6794e04","tid":1516534,"uid":37713,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"728e533a72b5278d192845bd39b38a1125d9272b","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5886902ba11ccb5b7e7938a1467d434d494e0c8c","tid":1516534,"uid":134774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":