arge;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"唉。。屋企全部都紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得我一條友黃"},{"pid":"ee80c4c20a00b4816ae2ca4d7d1fcbf9709d97e4","tid":1516534,"uid":161179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"同你個情況差唔多，我老母同呀哥偏藍，我同老豆就黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4490f99fcb4d83ccfd4922645595f68905d17129","tid":1516534,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee80c4c20a00b4816ae2ca4d7d1fcbf9709d97e4","tid":1516534,"uid":161179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"同你個情況差唔多，我老母同呀哥偏藍，我同老豆就黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"喺咁嘅環境生活 一定好痛苦"},{"pid":"87cb1aca19d4d635289c148efbe9cfdb09235886","tid":1516534,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"叫你老豆教育佢"},{"pid":"49e48e28111861f3a695076804b7411f7e573727","tid":1516534,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"細佬籃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0cba9576ef7511f365925889eaa9d55736bac0","tid":1516534,"uid":238706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b570a35d2fce850f81a14d43f0cf991455752522","tid":1516534,"uid":248558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"全屋得我同細佬黃，兩老係深藍，親戚全部深藍，簡直係人間煉獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"幸好 除左我媽同細路 全部黃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嫲70幾歲人發夢個陣仲夠膽個陣瞞住哂所有屋企人拎哂屋企啲傘出去遊行仲話去做勇武派<img src=\"/assets/